At lvl35, means like last December, this *sitting there and ask for not used drops* was an insider tip and no newbie new about it.<br>
<br>
I was there, sitting, not doing anything and very politely asking whether I could maybe loot a piece or two if noone needs them.<br>
Some very nice people said no and let the things rott. Thanks. But I repsected it, it was notmy kill and I had no right in looting it.<br>
Eventually I was able to get some gaunts and boots, that I still use.<br>
